Package: cnvAnalyzeR
Version: 0.99.2
Title: A comprehensive tool suite for CNV analysis
Author: Vinicius Henrique da Silva and Ludwig Geistlinger
Maintainer: Ludwig Geistlinger <Ludwig.Geistlinger@sph.cuny.edu>
Depends: 
    R(>= 3.5.0), 
